      "text": "- Upgrade CPU, RAM, disk, or network on one server\n- Usually easiest for early-stage systems\n- No major architecture change at first\n- Eventually hits hardware, cost, and failure limits",
      "fontSize": 17,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
