      "text": "Rule of thumb: vertical scaling buys simplicity.\nHorizontal scaling buys capacity and availability, but needs better architecture.",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Rule of thumb: vertical scaling buys simplicity.\nHorizontal scaling buys capacity and availability, but needs better architecture.",
