      "locked": false,
      "text": "A strong answer explains when each scaling style is useful,\nwhat breaks first, and which trade-off you are accepting.",
      "fontSize": 19,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A strong answer explains when each scaling style is useful,\nwhat breaks first, and which trade-off you are accepting.",
